      {
        "id": 19840803,
        "user_id": 1472254,
        "title": "Wolf Spider (Hogna Aspersa)",
        "description": "Working for AIMRL I was tasked with developing a set of virtual spiders that replicates the real-life motion of the spider in different environments.  AIMRL intends to use the virtual spider to train an AI to recognize a real spider, capture its movements and use the resulting data in unreal to then simulate and drive a micro-robot in the real world. I used Blender to develop models and environments. In combination with Unreal Engine to simulate the spider’s movement based off 30+ hand animated templates.  ",
        "created_at": "2025-01-29T13:15:19.738-06:00",
